name: Matrix
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
CantoSwap is the #1 NFT Marketplace and DEX on Canto.

Liquidity mining with Matrix rewards.
Stake Matrix tokens to receive a share of the dex trading fees.
Stake CantoPunks to earn Matrix.
1.25% of marketplace royalties used to buy and burn Matrix.
